    <!-- Policy Details -->
    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-pink max-w-none">
      
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-4">1. Cancellation by Customer</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">1.1 Timing-Based Refunds</h3>
        <p class="text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Refund amount depends on how far in advance you cancel before the scheduled service time:
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
          <div class="card p-6 border-l-4 border-green-500">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">More than 48 hours before service</h4>
            <p class="text-charcoal/80 text-sm">
              <strong>100% refund</strong> — Full refund of advance payment processed within 5-7 business days.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card p-6 border-l-4 border-green-400">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">24 to 48 hours before service</h4>
            <p class="text-charcoal/80 text-sm">
              <strong>75% refund</strong> — Partial refund to account for provider's lost opportunity.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card p-6 border-l-4 border-yellow-500">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">12 to 24 hours before service</h4>
            <p class="text-charcoal/80 text-sm">
              <strong>50% refund</strong> — Late cancellation impacts provider's scheduling significantly.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card p-6 border-l-4 border-orange-500">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">6 to 12 hours before service</h4>
            <p class="text-charcoal/80 text-sm">
              <strong>25% refund</strong> — Very late cancellation, minimal refund provided.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card p-6 border-l-4 border-red-500">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Less than 6 hours before service</h4>
            <p class="text-charcoal/80 text-sm">
              <strong>No refund</strong> — Too late for provider to fill the slot; advance payment is non-refundable.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">1.2 How to Cancel</h3>
        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-charcoal/80 ml-4 mb-4">
          <li>Go to your Customer Dashboard</li>
          <li>Find the booking under "Upcoming" or "Confirmed" tab</li>
          <li>Click "Cancel Booking"</li>
          <li>Confirm cancellation and provide reason (optional)</li>
          <li>Refund will be processed automatically based on timing</li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-4">2. Cancellation by Provider</h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          If a service provider cancels your confirmed booking:
        </p>
        <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-500 p-6 rounded-r-xl my-6">
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-charcoal/80">
            <li><strong>100% refund</strong> of your advance payment</li>
            <li>Refund processed within 1-2 business days</li>
            <li>You will receive an email notification with refund details</li>
            <li>Option to report the provider if cancellation was unreasonable</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p class="text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed">
          Note: Frequent provider cancellations may result in account suspension or removal from the platform.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-4">3. System Cancellations</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">3.1 Payment Timeout</h3>
        <p class="text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          If advance payment is not completed within 15 minutes of booking creation, the booking is automatically cancelled. 
          No refund is applicable as no payment was processed.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">3.2 Provider No-Show</h3>
        <p class="text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          If the provider doesn't show up for a confirmed booking:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-charcoal/80 ml-4 mb-4">
          <li>Report the no-show immediately via your dashboard</li>
          <li><strong>100% refund</strong> plus potential compensation</li>
          <li>Provider may face account suspension</li>
          <li>We will help you rebook with another provider if needed</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-4">4. Refund Process</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">4.1 How Refunds Are Processed</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-charcoal/80 ml-4 mb-4">
          <li>All refunds are processed through Razorpay to the original payment method</li>
          <li>Credit/debit card refunds: 5-7 business days</li>
          <li>UPI/wallet refunds: 3-5 business days</li>
          <li>Net banking refunds: 5-7 business days</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">4.2 Refund Confirmation</h3>
        <p class="text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          You will receive an email confirmation when:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-charcoal/80 ml-4 mb-4">
          <li>Refund is initiated (within 24 hours of cancellation)</li>
          <li>Refund is processed by Razorpay</li>
          <li>Refund reaches your bank/payment method</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-4">5. Non-Refundable Scenarios</h2>
        <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-6 rounded-r-xl my-6">
          <p class="text-charcoal/80 mb-4">
            <strong>No refund will be issued in the following cases:</strong>
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-charcoal/80">
            <li>Service has already started</li>
            <li>Service has been completed</li>
            <li>Cancellation within 6 hours of scheduled time</li>
            <li>Customer did not provide accurate address or was not available</li>
            <li>False claims or abuse of refund policy</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

